column1: #Text=Emmanuel Macron wins French presidential election race

#Text=candidate Emmanuel Macron won the second round of the 2017 French Presidential election , winning about 66.1 percent of the votes , defeating Front national ' s Marine Le Pen with the final result declared yesterday .
#Text=Winning the race with a significant vote difference , Marcon tweeted , " Everyone told us that it was impossible .
